snippet.title: Demeo | Announce Teaser
snippet.description:
RPG fans, unite… in virtual reality. A dark force has taken over the underworld in Resolution Games’ upcoming RPG dungeon crawler, Demeo, and it’s a world you’re not likely to survive alone. Coming in 2021. 

www.resolutiongames.com/demeo
https://reso.ly/demeo-steam
#Demeo #vrgame #quest2 #rift #steam #ResolutionGames #RPG
